{"ja504:0.1":"Jataka ","ja504:0.2":"Visatinipata ","ja504:0.3":"Matangavagga ","ja504:0.4":"8. Bhallatiyajataka ","ja504:1.1":"Bhallatiyo nama ahosi raja, ","ja504:1.2":"Rattham pahaya migavam acari so; ","ja504:1.3":"Agama girivaram gandhamadanam, ","ja504:1.4":"Supupphitam kimpurisanucinnam. ","ja504:2.1":"Salurasanghanca nisedhayitva, ","ja504:2.2":"Dhanum kalapanca so nikkhipitva; ","ja504:2.3":"Upagami vacanam vattukamo, ","ja504:2.4":"Yatthatthita kimpurisa ahesum. ","ja504:3.1":"“Himaccaye hemavataya tire, ","ja504:3.2":"Kimidhatthita mantayavho abhinham; ","ja504:3.3":"Pucchami vo manusadehavanne, ","ja504:3.4":"Katham vo jananti manussaloke”. ","ja504:4.1":"“Mallam girim pandarakam tikutam, ","ja504:4.2":"Sitodaka anuvicarama najjo; ","ja504:4.3":"Miga manussava nibhasavanna, ","ja504:4.4":"Jananti no kimpurisati ludda”. ","ja504:5.1":"“Sukiccharupam paridevayavho, ","ja504:5.2":"Alingito casi piyo piyaya; ","ja504:5.3":"Pucchami vo manusadehavanne, ","ja504:5.4":"Kimidha vane rodatha appatita. ","ja504:6.1":"Sukiccharupam paridevayavho, ","ja504:6.2":"Alingito casi piyo piyaya; ","ja504:6.3":"Pucchami vo manusadehavanne, ","ja504:6.4":"Kimidha vane vilapatha appatita. ","ja504:7.1":"Sukiccharupam paridevayavho, ","ja504:7.2":"Alingito casi piyo piyaya; ","ja504:7.3":"Pucchami vo manusadehavanne, ","ja504:7.4":"Kimidha vane socatha appatita”. ","ja504:8.1":"“Mayekarattam vippavasimha ludda, ","ja504:8.2":"Akamaka annamannam saranta; ","ja504:8.3":"Tamekarattam anutappamana, ","ja504:8.4":"Socama ‘sa ratti punam na hessati’”. ","ja504:9.1":"“Yamekarattam anutappathetam, ","ja504:9.2":"Dhanam va nattham pitaram va petam; ","ja504:9.3":"Pucchami vo manusadehavanne, ","ja504:9.4":"Katham vina vasamakappayittha”. ","ja504:10.1":"“Yamimam nadim passasi sighasotam, ","ja504:10.2":"Nanadumacchadanam selakulam; ","ja504:10.3":"Tam me piyo uttari vassakale, ","ja504:10.4":"Mamanca mannam anubandhatiti. ","ja504:11.1":"Ahanca ankolakamocinami, ","ja504:11.2":"Atimuttakam sattaliyothikanca; ","ja504:11.3":"‘Piyo ca me hehiti malabhari, ","ja504:11.4":"Ahanca nam malini ajjhupessam’. ","ja504:12.1":"Ahancidam kuravakamocinami, ","ja504:12.2":"Uddalaka patalisindhuvaraka; ","ja504:12.3":"‘Piyo ca me hehiti malabhari, ","ja504:12.4":"Ahanca nam malini ajjhupessam’. ","ja504:13.1":"Ahanca salassa supupphitassa, ","ja504:13.2":"Oceyya pupphani karomi malam; ","ja504:13.3":"‘Piyo ca me hehiti malabhari, ","ja504:13.4":"Ahanca nam malini ajjhupessam’. ","ja504:14.1":"Ahanca salassa supupphitassa, ","ja504:14.2":"Oceyya pupphani karomi bharam; ","ja504:14.3":"Idanca no hehiti santharattham, ","ja504:14.4":"Yatthajjimam viharissama rattim. ","ja504:15.1":"Ahanca kho agalum candananca, ","ja504:15.2":"Silaya pimsami pamattarupa; ","ja504:15.3":"‘Piyo ca me hehiti rositango, ","ja504:15.4":"Ahanca nam rosita ajjhupessam’. ","ja504:16.1":"Athagama salilam sighasotam, ","ja504:16.2":"Nudam sale salale kannikare; ","ja504:16.3":"Apuratha tena muhuttakena, ","ja504:16.4":"Sayam nadi asi maya suduttara. ","ja504:17.1":"Ubhosu tiresu mayam tada thita, ","ja504:17.2":"Sampassanta ubhayo annamannam; ","ja504:17.3":"Sakimpi rodama sakim hasama, ","ja504:17.4":"Kicchena no agama samvari sa. ","ja504:18.1":"Patova kho uggate suriyamhi, ","ja504:18.2":"Catukkam nadim uttariyana ludda; ","ja504:18.3":"Alingiya annamannam mayam ubho, ","ja504:18.4":"Sakimpi rodama sakim hasama. ","ja504:19.1":"Tihunakam sattasatani ludda, ","ja504:19.2":"Yamidha mayam vippavasimha pubbe; ","ja504:19.3":"Vassekimam jivitam bhumipala, ","ja504:19.4":"Ko nidha kantaya vina vaseyya”. ","ja504:20.1":"“Ayunca vo kivatako nu samma, ","ja504:20.2":"Sacepi janatha vadetha ayum; ","ja504:20.3":"Anussava vuddhato agama va, ","ja504:20.4":"Akkhatha me tam avikampamana”. ","ja504:21.1":"“Ayunca no vassasahassam ludda, ","ja504:21.2":"Na cantara papako atthi rogo; ","ja504:21.3":"Appanca dukkham sukhameva bhiyyo, ","ja504:21.4":"Avitaraga vijahama jivitam”. ","ja504:22.1":"“Idanca sutvana amanusanam, ","ja504:22.2":"Bhallatiyo ittara jivitanti; ","ja504:22.3":"Nivattatha na migavam acari, ","ja504:22.4":"Adasi danani abhunji bhoge. ","ja504:23.1":"Idanca sutvana amanusanam, ","ja504:23.2":"Sammodatha ma kalaham akattha; ","ja504:23.3":"Ma vo tapi attakammaparadho, ","ja504:23.4":"Yathapi te kimpurisekarattam. ","ja504:24.1":"Idanca sutvana amanusanam, ","ja504:24.2":"Sammodatha ma vivadam akattha; ","ja504:24.3":"Ma vo tapi attakammaparadho, ","ja504:24.4":"Yathapi te kimpurisekarattam”. ","ja504:25.1":"“Vividham adhimana sunomaham, ","ja504:25.2":"Vacanapatham tava atthasamhitam; ","ja504:25.3":"Muncam giram nudaseva me daram, ","ja504:25.4":"Samana sukhavaha jiva me ciran”ti. ","ja504:26.1":"Bhallatiyajatakam atthamam. "}